Exam administered during the midterm exam week.


2
Final Exam
40%
Exam administered during the final exam week.


3
End of Semester Writing Assignment
20%
Essay assignment on a choice of topics.





■  相關參考書目 (Other Useful Readings)The course instructor will comment on other useful readings--especially for students wishing to pursue graduate studies in the field--during the course of the semester.


