數位教材
開放式課程






















標題: 英國文學（二）English Literature II
作者: 趙順良Open Education Office開放教育推動中心
公開日期: 2010
摘要: 課程首頁
 
本課程是由交通大學外國語文物學系提供。
 
This course is a survey of English literature in the 19th and 20th centuries. Students will be introduced to the works of the major authors in the Romantic, Victorian, and Modernist periods in the history of English literature.課程目標/概述  
This course is a survey of English literature in the 19th and 20th centuries. Students will be introduced to the works of the major authors in the Romantic, Victorian, and Modernist periods in the history of English literature.　　
 
課程章節  



課程週次

單元主題

第一週
Introduction; The Romantic Period　

第二週
William Blake (1759-1827)

第三週
William Wordsworth (1770-1850)　

第四週
S. T. Coleridge (1772-1834)

第五週
Lord Byron (1788-1824) &amp; Percy Bysshe Shelley (1792-1822)

第六週
Shelley &amp; John Keats (1795-1821)


第七週
National Holiday: Tomb Sweeping Day 

第八週
lizabeth Browning (1806-61) &amp; Christina Rossetti (1830-94)

第九週

MID-TERM EXAM　 

第十週
Alfred, Lord Tennyson (1809-92) &amp; Charles Dickens (1812-70)

第十一週
Mathew Arnold (1822-88)

第十二週
Oscar Wilde (1854-1900)

第十三週
Modernist Manifestos

第十四週
W. B. Yeats (1865-1939)

第十五週
Virginia Woolf (1882-1941)

第十六週
ames Joyce (1882-1941) &amp; Doris Lessing (1919- )

第十七週
T. S. Eliot (1888-1965)　

第十八週
FINAL EXAM　

 
課程書目 
Stephen Greenblatt et al, eds. The Norton Anthology of English Literature. Vol. 2. 8th ed. New York and London: W. W. Norton, 2006.
 
